reviews.review_text: review? this is not a review...this site is for reviews, not jerry's personal life, which you could never have been a part of anyway...jerry was cool, and you are a nerd...go do some yoga   this show is another great one......excellent quality!

Frost : Best quality of the 3 here 5 stars for the quality of the recording Maybe some flaws in the playing (poor crazy fingers jam) (na) but this amazing recording reveals what a freak show the Frost was.  The electronic drum space preceeds chill out stuff you hear in the clubs today by more than 15 years.  It's the riff the kids used to sing during the interval:"On and on you can't stop the spirit it's like a mountain" that was the repoir btween band and fans '86 before the D.C. accident comes a time, IMHBTR, dancin' what a show. 1st set list strodinario! joking with Phil Jerry even spoke to the crowd!!!!!!!ahhaahah 
miracle us blues encore I mean c'mon 80's sound blast! I guess the 70's were cool but no grunge
